Features of Raspberry Pi Board:
1. Processor: ARM-based CPU (e.g., Quad-core Cortex-A72 for Pi 4).
2. Memory: 512MB to 8GB RAM (depending on the model).
3. Storage: MicroSD card slot for OS and data.
4. Graphics: Broadcom VideoCore GPU, HDMI output (up to 4K).
5. Connectivity: Ethernet, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth (varies by model).
6. I/O: 40 GPIO pins, USB ports, HDMI, Camera (CSI), Display (DSI).
7. Audio: 3.5mm jack or HDMI audio output.
8. Power: 5V USB power supply.

Available OS for Raspberry Pi:
1. Raspberry Pi OS (formerly Raspbian)
2. Ubuntu (Desktop/Server)
3. LibreELEC (Media center)
4. Osmc (Media center)
5. Windows 10 IoT Core
6. RetroPie (Gaming)
7. Kali Linux (Penetration testing)
8. DietPi (Lightweight OS)
9. Android (Mobile OS)

Program :
From gniozero import LED
From time import sleep
Led-LED(4)
While True:
Led On()
sleep(1)
Led Off
sleep(1)

